name: Containment Breach by Guillermo Del Toro

metadata.name: Containment Breach Edition #1
metadata.description: Bizarre nightmares unfold in a visually stunning, spine-tingling horror collection curated by Guillermo del Toro.Containment Breach is your entry into a world where each scene takes the holder through an exploration of all that comes alive after dark and all leading a first-of-its-kind horror experience where the holder is an integral part of each chapter.
